				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Hu%E1%BB%87/Ch%E1%BB%A9c-c%E1%BA%A9m-h%E1%BB%93i-v%C4%83n/poem-nF5ajtrF4j4zC0ZRfPADLA">Chức cẩm hồi văn - 織錦回文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B4-Hu%E1%BB%87/author-KOtVUs_kcoFrZTmRo_4QbA">Tô Huệ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/D%E1%BA%A1-t%C3%BAc-H%E1%BB%99i-An-ph%C3%B9ng-ch%E1%BB%A9c-ph%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-4X3Q60sKbi9_yaaN-B52uQ">Dạ túc Hội An phùng chức phường - 夜宿會安縫織坊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khi%E1%BA%BFu-N%C4%83ng-T%C4%A9nh/author-0k6qEpgf02Latsw5cZPrXg">Khiếu Năng Tĩnh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/Du-t%E1%BB%AD-ng%C3%A2m/poem-Y2JhRHKVghuiMb1ih5fI5g">Du tử ngâm - 遊子吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/M%E1%BA%A1nh-Giao/author-lb0C1LYxo0fcanV11dmAog">Mạnh Giao</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Li%E1%BB%85u-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%90%E1%BB%99ng-M%C3%A2n/poem-p2Tbcr9RpIrypCo8_q_ifw">Liễu Châu Động Mân - 柳州峒氓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/M%E1%BB%99ng-%C4%91%C4%83ng-H%C3%A0-H%C3%A1n/poem-bmNJwADre1PTjLamg-id0w">Mộng đăng Hà Hán - 夢登河漢</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Mai-Nghi%C3%AAu-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-LM0kb8TnwF3pXyZ2viD2Eg">Mai Nghiêu Thần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/Thi%C3%AAn-%C4%90%C3%B4-b%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91-ca/poem-AIgicgej92YFc1rwp6U4Cg">Thiên Đô bộc bố ca - 天都瀑布歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ti%E1%BB%81n-Khi%C3%AAm-%C3%8Dch/author-KdxnA4RirR7LsAi6oOaAoA">Tiền Khiêm Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Thi%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%A5n/poem-xfUL0RFU1M6WV9XOi__Sxg">Thiên vấn - 天問</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/Tr%C3%A1c-Ch%C3%A2u-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-b%C3%ADch/poem-0ejrayfUilPP9Fho8HBTuw">Trác Châu đề bích - 涿州題壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Huy-O%C3%A1nh/author-dr5ryihj5N63kZ-8HnRW6A">Nguyễn Huy Oánh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-T%C3%ADn-thu-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-VwvQemeJwpGd6rHhEcGfPA">Trường Tín thu từ kỳ 2 - 長信秋詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/author-Q_JpPOHTIyzNkB76eQk-WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/Xu%C3%A2n-quang/poem-zpzsRYsqsphQiAOK3LRqkA">Xuân quang - 春光</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0-Nh%C6%B0/author-mhAlF-W1JHQDMsH_S0aV3Q">Hà Như</a>)<br></div>	</div>
